{"tid":764894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水大叔爭減價貨　嘈到瞓地","createTime":"2018-08-02T10:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T10:55:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed73ad86c9c1bb86e3d0b30c8d0d7c0e57e53001","tid":764894,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20467064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20467064&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudscn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6d204c52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180802%2F20467064&h=a3cb9346\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180802/20467064</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02日 <br />\n<br />\n上水大叔爭減價貨　嘈到瞓地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上水彩園商場一間體育用品店準備搬遷，推出大減價優惠清貨，昨日最後一日營業，一度吸引數十名街坊排隊搶購貨品，其間懷疑有人插隊，引起其他人不滿並發生爭執，雙方繼而互相推撞，一名中年男子倒地躺卧地上，最終需由警方到場解決事件。<br />\n<br />\n現場為上水彩園商場3樓一間體育用品店，店舖主要售賣波鞋及運動服裝，近日打算搬遷前清貨，於是推出大減價優惠，為免店內人多雜亂，店家讓街坊排隊分批進店購物。昨午約1時許，約60名街坊趁店舖最後一日營業到場搶購，排隊期間一名中年男子被質疑插隊，引起排隊人士不滿。<br />\n<br />\n雙方初生口角越吵越烈，令現場出現混亂，繼而更動互相推撞，被指插隊的中年漢突然躺在地上，其他人則繼續排隊。商場保安聞訊到場視察中年漢情況，並維持秩序，警員亦接報到場調查，經了解後無人被捕，列糾紛案處理。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n過路男捱貨車撞　頭傷淌血送院<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n文化人物：IT男厭倦呃like　死場開無人書店 (呂麗嬋)"},{"pid":"4153af64874f9e2e7d584d9aee92f8cbebc24a03","tid":764894,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea09f98213b60e27aec9257d8f90358f4caf608b","tid":764894,"uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/a7JOnZXj0ezNC/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia3.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2Fa7JOnZXj0ezNC%2Fgiphy.gif&h=0d33adcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1967754a1d96d8eb0d5a784afdf02e7fb17f9190","tid":764894,"uid":179503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c88a79ffde3120b08cbf1596385e6ee65a39cdf2","tid":764894,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T10:55:34.000Z","msg":"廢老！<br />\n<br />\n打架不忘sleep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}